- cs.LG (Machine Learning) is another possible category as the paper uses a neural network classifier as a feature extractor. 
- cs.MM (Multimedia) is a potential category as the paper deals with fashion images. 
- cs.CL (Computation and Language) is less likely but still possible as the paper discusses content-based recommendation systems.
